:

1. *Stana* je veoma lijepa i udobna za život. (The apartment is very nice and comfortable to live in.)
2. On je preselio u tu *stanu* pre nekoliko mjeseci. (He moved into that apartment a few months ago.)
3. Oni su se opremili *stanom* odmah nakon što su se vjenčali. (They furnished the apartment right after they got married.)
4. *Stanu* je potrebno mnogo popravka. (The apartment needs a lot of repairs.)
5. Ona je završila zadatke u *stanu*. (She finished the tasks in the apartment.)
6. Oni su iznajmili *stanu* na godinu dana. (They rented the apartment for one year.)